# CODEOWNERS - Define code ownership for parallel development
# Each story has clear ownership to minimize merge conflicts
#
# Format: <pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Use GitHub usernames (e.g., @username) or team names (e.g., @org/team)

# =============================================================================
# GLOBAL OWNERS (for files that affect everyone)
# =============================================================================

# Root config files - require review from tech lead
/*.json                         @tech-lead
/*.js                           @tech-lead
/*.yaml                         @tech-lead
/.github/                       @tech-lead

# Documentation - anyone can contribute
/docs/                          @tech-lead
*.md                            @tech-lead

